{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-15", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "千瘡百孔", "storyInfo": "經歷了漫長歲月的變形者集群向年輕的女妖之主敞開了心扉。隨著酒店的一場大火，諾伯特區的真正的亂局才終於開始。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibtownn", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magicchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次是伊比利亞。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耐心些，女妖，我在這裡的日子最難忘。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為你不會喜歡那裡。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那場災難發生之前，我確實不喜歡伊比利亞。那些誇誇其談和自以為是讓我膩煩透了。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們不懂得畏懼。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，那場災難讓你滿足了嗎？", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是老紅眼病那樣的心理變態，災難本身也沒什麼出奇，這片大地何時缺少過災難？", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那些生物讓我著迷。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是聽說過一些傳聞，說實話，那些東西讓我十分不安。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們與我們過於迥異。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你認為我與你迥異嗎，女妖？", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該知道，無論是哪種樣子，都不是真正的我。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石在所有人的身上都留下了無可辯駁的烙印，它讓你們以現有的樣子在世間行走。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可它唯獨忘記了變形者。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯獨我們仍然保存了最初生時的樣子。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會為你的純潔自豪嗎？", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不，當這個世界都已變了樣子，純潔又還有什麼意義？", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能追趕它帶來的變化，我只能追趕你們。追趕你們所創造的一切。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我用盡了各種辦法，我在伊比利亞發現了一個荒廢的鎮子，我住了進去。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們住了進去。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們讓那座鎮子重新運行起來，工作，交流，商業，交通......", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩百個我組成了一個小鎮。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道你至今都沒有陷入瘋狂，是你的幸運還是不幸。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，誰知道呢。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，我在那裡度過了印象深刻的一段時光，有那麼多的事情要處理，我每天沉溺其中。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這給我帶來了一種錯覺，我們過得有意義。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，疲乏最終還是到來了，專注於瑣事很有趣，但是就算把它們全部加起來，依然無法讓我找到答案。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到我發現了它們，我聽有的人稱呼那些東西為“海嗣”。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我觀察了它們很久。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們讓你想到了自己。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，論統一，我們超過了海嗣和它們的那些大群。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論分化為多少形貌，我們始終是統一的，而海嗣，它們只能選擇投入大群。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，你知道嗎，我羡慕它們。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們只需要遵循本能就夠了。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尋找食物，尋找養分，繁衍，進化。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，你剛剛所說的，“純潔”這個詞，應該放在它們身上。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我，我留在原地，看著這一切，看著那些多姿多彩的小生物把一片海草同化為它們的一員。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們什麼都不想，它們做自己該做的事。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們呢，我們的本能是什麼？我們又該做什麼？", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女妖，你能給我們什麼建議？", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在笑嗎？", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，變形者，我並非在嘲笑你。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位可稱最古老的王庭之主的變形者閣下，只是在尋找他生活的意義。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這很重要，這當然很重要，我只是沒想過，站在我面前的，原來是個彷徨的哲學家。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你猜，我們在維多利亞的大學當了幾年哲學教授？", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於你們而言，尋找意義是簡單的，除去那極少部分存在，生命總可稱得上短暫。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為自己尋找到一個目標，用以填滿這些時光沒那麼難。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們不行。", "name": "“伊比利亞人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_mini02_victoria_street_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magicchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是你的提議，還是特雷西斯的未來，我們都沒什麼興趣。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於我們而言，都是打發時間罷了。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們為什麼要對這些轉瞬即逝的東西抱有感情呢？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們幾乎窮盡了一切可能，我們也幾乎窮盡了一切樂趣。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我開始可憐你了，變形者。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你發現了我們只是個喊著什麼都沒勁透了的老傢伙。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道這個秘密的人可不多。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的幾個朋友教過我一種愚蠢的遊戲......", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，還是算了。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說說吧，女妖，我們比你猜的要有興趣。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，或許得等等了，有個麻煩的工作找上門了。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是在這裡，但我們恐怕還是得分點心。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g6_hotellobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有......是什麼意思？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有就是沒有，該死的！", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#3$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通訊站不在那裡，那裡什麼也沒有，有人搶先了！", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#3$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是那些深池的部隊嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#15$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕還要早得多。根據灰塵的厚度判斷，諾伯特區剛駛離倫蒂尼姆的時候，就有人盯上那裡了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位赤鐵近衛隊的隊長不會真的被我們騙過去的，他很快就會發現預計的通訊沒有發出。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但最起碼，我們又回到同一條起跑線了，大家重新有了賺獎金的機會。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是服務於開斯特公爵的你，還是深池的鬼魂部隊......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們都以秘密潛入的方式進入這個地塊，這就說明了，你們想維持諾伯特區表面上的現狀。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 1