{"content": "我在這裡度過了很美好的時光，我在這裡認識了些很不錯的人。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#2$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾伯特區是個生機勃勃的好地方，別讓它就這麼淪為回憶和廢墟。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#2$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老先生，我們會的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陰謀與紛爭終會消弭。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一位......我十分十分想念的人和我說過......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許有一天......這片大地上的每一個人，都能平靜入夢。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真是折騰，這家酒店又亂了幾分。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#7$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不親自打掃的人，總是不知道保持一點秩序有多不容易。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#7$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "珀茜瓦爾！珀茜瓦爾！", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她又跑到哪裡去了......", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，就讓我這個老傢伙自己待一會兒吧。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位年邁的酒店經理找來了一張同樣年邁的扶手椅，選了個舒服的姿勢坐了進去。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她......那個卡特斯女孩，就是魔王嗎？", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "追上這些變化越來越難了，就連我都要為此吃驚。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變化......變化，也許我怠惰於這種變化了吧。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變化畢竟不是前進。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，也該告別這位老朋友了，說實話......我真的很喜歡這裡。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......考伯特該再堅持兩個月的，誰能想到呢，兩個月後，薩卡茲的軍隊進了城，一個魔族佬也能從清潔員變成酒店經理呢。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我總是弄不懂這些。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲老人站起身來，巡視著酒店的大堂，這裡的每一件物品都與他息息相關。"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個叫伊內絲的卡普里尼說，戰爭不配用任何修飾。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，就讓我們還原它本來的面貌吧。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_lighter", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在不知被多少政要貴族踏上過的精美編織地毯上，薩卡茲老人丟下一枚點燃的打火機。"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$b_char_fireharm", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$fireburst", "loop": "false", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.3, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.8, "g": 0.3, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_burn", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨即，火焰熊熊升起。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "bgEffect", "attributes": {"layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g5_blockadewall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡......這些士兵，都被殺死了？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#8$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是敵人嗎？！如果我早些發現的話......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#8$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的家屬會收到撫恤金，如果有家屬的話。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們必須防備......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#5$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的那副表情......你早就知道？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#8$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......這也是你計劃的一部分......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是卡茲戴爾軍事委員會的安排。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雇傭兵，犧牲是在所難免的，我以為你的隊長早就教過你這一點。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是個將軍，他們是你的士兵！", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#5$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我是個將軍，這就是我的工作。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是我們的敵人還是我們自己，需要做的事情就是把一個個生命投進這個名為戰爭的巨口中——", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並祈禱它能吐出讓我們稱心如意的結果。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是以我的立場能做的所有行為。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#10$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我會過來，我會過來注視著這一切。看過這裡每一張年輕的蒼白的臉龐。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須牢記，這是我做出的決定。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會說這是薩卡茲不得不付出的代價，雇傭兵。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞人殺死了他們，但是是我讓他們被維多利亞人殺死。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼要這樣做？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#10$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了點燃火焰。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "點燃一場遍及這片大地的火焰。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們......薩卡茲，唯有在這樣一片紛爭的大地上，才有可能找到自己的位置，找到自己生存的空間。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雇傭兵，你必須學會熟悉它。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "熟悉它，憎恨它，最後接受它。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為這是唯一的辦法。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$firestorm", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一團明亮的火焰猛然在封鎖區中升起，老舊的大樓在熊熊燃燒。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又是......火災嗎？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#8$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，那是第一簇火苗。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雇傭兵，跟我來吧，我們需要回到飛空艇上。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客人們都已經入席了。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}